com.acrolinx.javasdk.api.validation

Class Preconditions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acrolinx.javasdk.api.validation.Preconditions

  • public final class Preconditions
extends Object
    The class Preconditions is used to check if parameters and states are in the expected state. You can configure the preconditions by setPreconditionFailureHandling(PreconditionFailureHandling) and the system property PRECONDITION_FAILURE_HANDLING_SYSTEM_PROPERTY.

      The enum PreconditionFailureHandling provides different strategies for handling precondition failures.
